      <title>Sovcomflot承认困难，俄罗斯石油紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/russian-oil-squeeze-tightens-as-sovcomflot-admits-difficulties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国家油轮公司PJSC Sovcomflot表示，美国的制裁正在对其运营施加压力，这是这些措施导致该国石油运输复杂化的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/russian-oil-squeeze-tightens-as-sovcomflot-admits-difficulties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
