      <title>巴克莱银行希望通过主权财富基金推动IB业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/barclays-looks-to-sovereign-wealth-funds-in-ib-push-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行首席执行官 C.S. Venkatakrishnan 表示，该银行希望扩大与主权财富基金和私募股权巨头的关系，以扩大其在咨询和股票承销领域的业务。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/barclays-looks-to-sovereign-wealth-funds-in-ib-push-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌计划剥离 1,000 个零售店，转向电动汽车充电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/shell-plans-to-divest-1-000-retail-sites-in-shift-to-ev-charging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司计划在未来两年内每年剥离 500 个零售站点，以满足对电动汽车充电器不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/shell-plans-to-divest-1-000-retail-sites-in-shift-to-ev-charging</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
